data.description: ** OPEN HOUSE SUN 12/10 FROM 12-3PM **Modern urban living in the highly sought out Lavaca community, conveniently located near King William, Southtown, The San Antonio Riverwalk, Alamodome, major expressways, breweries, art museums, night life, and so much more! This one-of-a-kind home features a private front patio where you can enjoy sipping your morning coffee or cool evening sunsets. Fantastic curb appeal invites you from the road, then upon entrance you are greeted by luxurious stained concrete flooring throughout entire home. A neutral color palette and recessed lighting enhance front living area, then soaring kitchen ceilings in the heart of the home highlight a stunning view of the backyard with oversized windows, stainless steel appliances, an island, custom cabinetry, and abundant natural light. Home also offers a workshop for hobbies, projects, or additional storage space! An exquisite outdoor sanctuary provides a generous covered patio adorned with ceiling fans, a delightful water fountain, a dedicated gardening area, a freshly installed privacy fence, and breathtaking landscaping. This stunning property is powered by a high-end and fully-owned 8.4 kw solar system with battery backup. Currently STR-permitted!
